sequenceDiagram
  participant User as User
  participant UI as Web UI
  participant API as FastAPI API
  participant Safety as Input Boundary
  participant Storage as Ephemeral Storage
  participant Worker as Analysis Worker

  User->>UI: Choose upload or public URL
  UI->>User: Ask for consent confirmation
  UI->>API: POST /analyses
  API->>Safety: Validate type, size, consent, URL target
  Safety-->>API: Accepted media packet
  API->>Storage: Store short-lived encrypted blob
  API->>Worker: Queue or background analysis
  Worker->>Storage: Read media for analysis
  Worker-->>API: Store result and report state
  API-->>UI: Status and final report
  User->>API: DELETE /analyses/{id}
  API->>Storage: Remove remaining media/report state
